# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Large local assets — NEVER commit these.
#
# _original-photos/ is ~353 MB of full-resolution JPEGs. GitHub warns above
# 50 MB per file and rejects at 100 MB, and anything committed here would live
# in git history forever, making every future clone drag the full 353 MB down.
# The web-ready derivatives in images/ (5.9 MB) are what actually ship.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
_original-photos/
images/Website/

# The original Claude design-canvas prototype. Kept for reference; not shipped.
_prototype/

# Old nested working folder — superseded by the files at the repo root.
Susana's Family Photography/

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Secrets.
# The Supabase ANON key in js/config.js is public by design and IS committed —
# it is protected by Row Level Security. The SERVICE ROLE key bypasses RLS and
# must never appear anywhere in this repo.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env*.local

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/

# Tooling
node_modules/
.vercel
.env*
dist/
node_modules/
